exceptions.exn: In environment L : Language M : Model T : System L value : nat -> U M H : forall f : Formula L, mem (Formula L) T f -> interpFormula value (nnTranslate f) Unable to unify "(fix interpFormula (value : nat -> U M) (f : Formula L) {struct f} : Prop := match f with | @equal _ t s => interpTerm value t = interpTerm value s | @atomic _ r ts => interpRels (arity L (inl r)) (rel M r) value ts | @impH _ A B => interpFormula value A -> interpFormula value B | @notH _ A => interpFormula value A -> False | @forallH _ v A => forall x : U M, interpFormula (updateValue value v x) A end) value (nnTranslate ?M1420)" with "exists f : Formula L, ~ SysPrf L T f".
